","msg":"成個post無人講blame the victim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a361d97482a1cb85e3c465fb4ea79558989aaf","tid":309040,"uid":17510,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:31:35.000Z","msg":"不虞有詐 不疑有詐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因涉嫌販運700噸毒品而被政府檢控，繼而棄保潛逃到台灣惟持假證入境遭台警逮捕兼入獄一年與及成為本港頭號通緝犯，亦使自己終身未能返港，及後多次哀求政府撤銷通緝令不果，最終客死異鄉並經常被網民恥笑的東方日報創辦人馬惜珍，其所創辦的東方日報旗下啲記者係咪唔撚識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6edb90e67eb3378f90c99027759a5f6a74719d","tid":309040,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219ba2549847a4bc126b0775398094f515941389","tid":309040,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T20:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61ecb99be852ff3d3862aebcaec80206079eea5f","tid":309040,"uid":960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T21:39:50.000Z","msg":"之前400蚊有粒intel 8核cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差啲中伏<br />\n睇過曬原來簡體字來，即刻留comment提其他人<br />\n唔知仲有冇港豬中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0cc17884705ea2defcd5aa28bcfb342d52249b","tid":309040,"uid":14797,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T21:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>599 買3TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平到爛</blockquote><br />\n600買3TB好正常<br />\n你知唔知價<img src=\"/assets/fac